import React,{Component} from 'react' var mealtypeurl = "http://localhost:8900/mealtype"; class QuickSearchDisplay extends Component{ constructor(){ super() this.state={ mealtype:"" } } render(){ return(
{this.handleQuickCards(this)}
) } componentDidMount(){ fetch(mealtypeurl,{method:'GET'}).then((res) => res.json()).then((data) => { console.log(data) }) } } export default QuickSearchDisplay
